--[ Version 1.2 / 2010-06-08 / MAJA ]----------------------------------------

* Added DBI to the list of dependencies.

---[ Version 1.1 / 2009-11-16 / MAJA ]---------------------------------------

+ added argument 'nameservers' which allows to specify a list of DNS
  forwarders instead of using the nameservers defined in /etc/resolv.conf

+ added nameservers_port option, which lets you specify the remote nameservers
  port.

+ added uid/gid and nameserver commandline argument to dns-proxy.pl

---[ Version 1.0 / 2009-11-15 / MAJA ]---------------------------------------

+ Initial Release

